    <text>
        <body>
            <entry xml:id="entry_kocora" xml:lang="os">
                <form type="lemma"><orth>kocora</orth><form type="variant"
                        ><orth>gocora</orth></form><form type="variant"
                        ><orth>cokora</orth></form><form type="variant"
                    ><orth>ʒokora</orth></form></form>
                <sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>кудри</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>curls</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>чуб</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>forelock</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>кисть на башлыке</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>tassel on a bashlyk</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense></sense>
                <abv:exampleGrp>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>syǧzærin gocoraǵyn læppū</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>златокудрый мальчик</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>golden-haired boy</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_СОПам."/><biblScope xml:lang="ru">IV 46
                                сл.</biblScope><biblScope xml:lang="en">IV 46 ff.</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                </abv:exampleGrp>
                <etym xml:lang="ru">Из <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><lang/>
                        <w>kočori</w>
                        <gloss><q>чуб</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>хохол</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ka"
                            ><w>kočora</w>
                        <gloss><q>чубатый</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>хохлатый</q></gloss></mentioned>; форма %icokora%i — результат
                    метатезы; формы %igocora%i, %iʒokora%i дают диссимилятивное озвончение
                    начального согласного (см. <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Ахвледиани"
                        /></bibl>).</etym>
                <etym xml:lang="en">From <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><lang/>
                        <w>kočori</w>
                        <gloss><q>forelock</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>topknot</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ka"
                            ><w>kočora</w>
                        <gloss><q>with a forelock</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>with topknots</q></gloss></mentioned>; the form %icokora%i is a
                    result of a metathesis; the forms %igocora%i, %iʒokora%i give dissimilative
                    vocalization of the initial consonant (see <bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_Ахвледиани"/></bibl>).</etym>
            </entry>
